Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User adam.dickison@posteo.net
PassCmd "kp get mail/posteo.de"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.local/mail/adam.dickison@posteo.net/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/adam.dickison@posteo.net/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Patterns *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User adam.dickison@gmail.com
PassCmd "kp get mail/google-mbsync"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.local/mail/adam.dickison@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/.local/mail/adam.dickison@gmail.com/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
